    "Second, labor mobility is low within Japanese universities.",
    "Third, apprenticeship relations in Japan often last for a lifetime\".",
    "Butler et al. (2018) did not focus on HCRs from a specific country, but from a specific discipline.",
    "The results are, however, also relevant for interpreting the results for other disciplines.",
    "The authors investigated a sample of 29 HCRs from the 2017 HCRs list in \"Social Sciences, general\"."
